                "category": "defensive",
                "deathNote": true,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Each time the divine warden army loses a segment and when they're reduced to 0 Hit Points, divine energy erupts from the fallen, dealing @Damage[8d6[spirit]|options:area-damage] damage to each enemy within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:30] (@Check[will|dc:38|basic] save). On a failure, a creature is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 1 day (@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
                },
